6 (תֹּכֶן);","strongs_def":"Token, a place in Palestine","kjv_def":"Tochen."},"H8508":{"id":"H8508","lemma":"תׇּכְנִית","translit":"toknîyth","pron":"tok-neeth'","derivation":"from H8506 (תֹּכֶן);","strongs_def":"admeasurement, i.e. consummation","kjv_def":"pattern, sum.","pos":"feminine noun","usage":"sum(1x), pattern(1x)"},"H8509":{"id":"H8509","lemma":"תַּכְרִיךְ","translit":"takrîyk","pron":"tak-reek'","derivation":"apparently from an unused root meaning to encompass;","strongs_def":"a wrapper or robe","kjv_def":"garment.","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"garment(1x)"},"H8510":{"id":"H8510","lemma":"תֵּל","translit":"têl","pron":"tale","derivation":"by contraction from H8524 (תָּלַל);","strongs_def":"a mound","kjv_def":"heap, [idiom] strength.","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"heap(4x), strength(1x)"},"H8511":{"id":"H8511","lemma":"תָּלָא","translit":"tâlâʼ","pron":"taw-law'","derivation":"a primitive root;","strongs_def":"to suspend; figuratively (through hesitation) to be uncertain; by implication (of mental dependence) to habituate","kjv_def":"be bent, hang (in doubt).","pos":"verb","usage":"hang(2x), bent(1x)"},"H8512":{"id":"H8512","lemma":"תֵּל אָבִיב","translit":"Têl ʼÂbîyb","pron":"tale aw-beeb'","derivation":"from H8510 (תֵּל) and H24 (אָבִיב); mound of green growth;","strongs_def":"Tel-Abib, a place in Chaldaea","kjv_def":"Tel-abib.","pos":"proper locative noun","usage":"Telabib(1x)"},"H8513":{"id":"H8513","lemma":"תְּלָאָה","translit":"tᵉlâʼâh","pron":"tel-aw-aw'","derivation":"from H3811 (לָאָה);","strongs_def":"distress","kjv_def":"travail, travel, trouble.","pos":"feminine noun","usage":"travel(2x), travail(1x), trouble(1x)"},"H8514":{"id":"H8514","lemma":"תַּלְאוּבָה","translit":"talʼûwbâh","pron":"tal-oo-baw'","derivation":"from H3851 (לַהַב);","strongs_def":"desiccation","kjv_def":"great drought."},"H8515":{"id":"H8515","lemma":"תְּלַאשַּׂר","translit":"Tᵉlaʼssar","pron":"tel-as-sar'","derivation":"or תְּלַשַּׂר; of foreign derivation;","strongs_d