;","strongs_def":"an erection, i.e. pillar (probably for a guide-board)","kjv_def":"high heap.","pos":"masculine noun"},"H8565":{"id":"H8565","lemma":"תַּן","translit":"tan","pron":"tan","derivation":"from an unused root probably meaning to elongate;","strongs_def":"a monster (as preternaturally formed), i.e. a sea-serpent (or other huge marine animal); also a jackal (or other hideous land animal)","kjv_def":"dragon, whale. Compare H8577 (תַּנִּין).","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"whale(1x)"},"H8566":{"id":"H8566","lemma":"תָּנָה","translit":"tânâh","pron":"taw-naw'","derivation":"a primitive root;","strongs_def":"to present (a mercenary inducement), i.e. bargain with (a harlot)","kjv_def":"hire.","pos":"verb","usage":"hired(2x)"},"H8567":{"id":"H8567","lemma":"תָּנָה","translit":"tânâh","pron":"taw-naw'","derivation":"a primitive root (identical with through the idea of attributing honor);","strongs_def":"to ascribe (praise), i.e. celebrate, commemorate","kjv_def":"lament, rehearse.","pos":"verb","usage":"lament(1x), rehearse(1x)"},"H8568":{"id":"H8568","lemma":"תַּנָּה","translit":"tannâh","pron":"tan-naw'","derivation":"probably feminine of H8565 (תַּן);","strongs_def":"a female jackal","kjv_def":"dragon.","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"dragon(1x)"},"H8569":{"id":"H8569","lemma":"תְּנוּאָה","translit":"tᵉnûwʼâh","pron":"ten-oo-aw'","derivation":"from H5106 (נוּא);","strongs_def":"alienation; by implication, enmity","kjv_def":"breach of promise, occasion.","pos":"feminine noun","usage":"occasion(1x)"},"H8570":{"id":"H8570","lemma":"תְּנוּבָה","translit":"tᵉnûwbâh","pron":"ten-oo-baw'","derivation":"from H5107 (נוּב);","strongs_def":"produce","kjv_def":"fruit, increase.","pos":"feminine noun","usage":"fruit(3x), increase(2x)"},"H8571":{"id":"H8571","lemma":"תְּנוּךְ","translit":"tᵉnûwk","pron":"ten-ook'","derivation":"perhaps from the same as H594 (אֲנָךְ) through the idea of protraction;","strongs_def":"a pinnacle, i.e. extremity","kjv_def":"tip.","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"tip(8x)"},"H8572":{"id":"H8572","lemma":"תְּנוּמָה","translit":"tᵉnûwmâh","pron":"ten-oo-maw'","derivation":"from H5123 (נוּם);","strongs_def":"drowsiness, i.e. sleep","kjv_def":"slumber(-ing).","pos":"feminine noun","usage":"slumber(4x), slumbering(1x)"},"H8573":{"id":"H8573","lemma":"תְּנוּפָה","translit":"tᵉnûwphâh","pron":"ten-oo-faw'","derivation":"from H5130 (נוּף);","strongs_def":"a brandishing (in threat); by implication, tumult; specifically, the official undulation of sacrificial offerings","kjv_def":"offering, shaking, wave (offering).","pos":"feminine noun","usage":"wave(8x), offering(6x), shaking(2x)"},"H8574":{"id":"H8574","lemma":"תַּנּוּר","translit":"tannûwr","pron":"tan-noor'","derivation":"from H5216 (נִיר);","strongs_def":"a fire-pot","kjv_def":"furnace, oven.","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"oven(11x), furnace(4x)"},"H8575":{"id":"H8575","lemma":"תַּנְחוּם","translit":"tanchûwm","pron":"tan-khoom'","derivation":"or תַּנְחֻם; and (feminine) תַּנְחוּמָה; from H5162 (נָחַם);","strongs_def":"compassion, solace","kjv_def":"comfort, consolation.","pos":"masculine/feminine noun","usage":"consolation(4x), comfort(1x)"},"H8576":{"id":"H8576","lemma":"תַּנְחֻמֶת","translit":"Tanchumeth","pron":"tan-khoo'-meth","derivation":"for H8575 (תַּנְחוּם) (feminine);","strongs_def":"Tanchumeth, an Israelite","kjv_def":"Tanhumeth.","pos":"proper masculine noun","usage":"Tanhumeth(2x)"},"H8577":{"id":"H8577","lemma":"תַּנִּין","translit":"tannîyn","pron":"tan-neen'","derivation":"or תַּנִּים; (Ezekiel 29:3), intensive from the same as H8565 (תַּן);","strongs_def":"a marine or land monster, i.e. sea-serpent or jackal","kjv_def":"dragon, sea-monster, serpent, whale.","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"dragon(21x), serpent(3x), whale(3x)"},"H8578":{"id":"H8578","lemma":"תִּנְיָן","translit":"tinyân","pron":"tin-yawn'","derivation":"(Aramaic) corresponding to H8147 (שְׁנַיִם);","strongs_def":"second","kjv_def":"second.","pos":"adjective","usage":"second(1x)"},"H8579":{"id":"H8579","lemma":"תִּנְיָנוּת","translit":"tinyânûwth","pron":"tin-yaw-nooth'","derivation":"(Aramaic) from H8578 (תִּנְיָן);","strongs_def":"a second time","kjv_def":"again.","pos":"adverb","usage":"again(1x)"},"H8580":{"id":"H8580","lemma":"תַּנְשֶׁמֶת","translit":"tanshemeth","pron":"tan-sheh'-meth","derivation":"from H5395 (נָשַׁם);","strongs_def":"properly, a hard breather, i.e. the name of two unclean creatures, a lizard and abird (both perhaps from changing color through their irascibility), probably the tree-toad and the water-hen","kjv_def":"mole, swan.","pos":"feminine noun","usage":"swan(2x), mole(1x)"},"H8581":{"id":"H8581","lemma":"תַּעָב","translit":"taʻâb","pron":"taw-ab'","derivation":"a primitive root;","strongs_def":"to loathe, i.e. (morally) detest","kjv_def":"(make to be) abhor(-red), (be, commit more, do) abominable(-y), [idiom] utterly.","pos":"verb","usage":"abhor(14x), abominable(6x), abominably(1x), utterly(1x)"},"H8582":{"id":"H8582","lemma":"תָּעָה","translit":"tâʻâh","pron":"taw-aw'","derivation":"a primitive root;","strongs_def":"to vacillate, i.e. reel or stray (literally or figuratively); also causative of both","kjv_def":"(cause to) go astray, deceive, dissemble, (cause to, make to) err, pant, seduce, (make to) stagger, (cause to) wander, be out of the way.","pos":"verb","usage":"err(17x), astray(12x), wander(10x), seduced(3x), stagger(2x), away(1x), deceived(1x)"},"H8583":{"id":"H8583","lemma":"תֹּעוּ","translit":"Tôʻûw","pron":"to'-oo","derivation":"or תֹּעִי; from H8582 (תָּעָה); error","strongs_def":"Tou or Toi, a Syrian king","kjv_def":"Toi, Tou."},"H8584":{"id":"H8584","lemma":"תְּעוּדָה","translit":"tᵉʻûwdâh","pron":"teh-oo-daw'","derivation":"from H5749 (עוּד);","strongs_def":"attestation, i.e. a precept, usage","kjv_def":"testimony.","pos":"feminine noun","usage":"testimony(3x)"},"H8585":{"id":"H8585","lemma":"תְּעָלָה","translit":"tᵉʻâlâh","pron":"teh-aw-law'","derivation":"from H5927 (עָלָה);","strongs_def":"a channel (into which water is raised for irrigation); also a bandage or plaster (as placed upon a wound)","kjv_def":"conduit, cured, healing, little river, trench, watercourse.","pos":"feminine noun","usage":"conduit(4x), trench(3x), watercourse(1x), healing(1x), cured(1x)"},"H8586":{"id":"H8586","lemma":"תַּעֲלוּל","translit":"taʻălûwl","pron":"tah-al-ool'","derivation":"from H5953 (עָלַל);","strongs_def":"caprice (as a fit coming on), i.e. vexation; concretely a tyrant","kjv_def":"babe, delusion.","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"babe(1x), delusion(1x)"},"H8587":{"id":"H8587","lemma":"תַּעֲלֻמָּה","translit":"taʻălummâh","pron":"tah-al-oom-maw'","derivation":"from H5956 (עָלַם);","strongs_def":"a secret","kjv_def":"thing that is hid, secret.","pos":"feminine noun","usage":"secret(2x)"},"H8588":{"id":"H8588","lemma":"תַּעֲנוּג","translit":"taʻănûwg","pron":"tah-an-oog'","derivation":"or תַּעֲנֻג; and (feminine) תַּעֲנֻגָה; from H6026 (עָנַג);","strongs_def":"luxury","kjv_def":"delicate, delight, pleasant.","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"delight(3x), delicate(1x), pleasant(1x)"},"H8589":{"id":"H8589","lemma":"תַּעֲנִית","translit":"taʻănîyth","pron":"tah-an-eeth'","derivation":"from H6031 (עָנָה);","strongs_def":"affliction (of self), i.e. fasting","kjv_def":"heaviness.","pos":"feminine noun","usage":"heaviness(1x)"},"H8590":{"id":"H8590","lemma":"תַּעֲנָךְ","translit":"Taʻănâk","pron":"tah-an-awk'","derivation":"or תַּעְנָךְ; of uncertain derivation;","strongs_def":"Taanak or Tanak, a place in Palestine","kjv_def":"Taanach, Tanach.","pos":"proper locative noun","usage":"Taanach(6x), Tanach(1x)"},"H8591":{"id":"H8591","lemma":"תָּעַע","translit":"tâʻaʻ","pron":"taw-ah'","derivation":"a primitive root;","strongs_def":"to cheat; by analogy, to maltreat","kjv_def":"deceive, misuse.","pos":"verb","usage":"deceiver(1x), misused(1x)"},"H8592":{"id":"H8592","lemma":"תַּעֲצֻמָה","translit":"taʻătsumâh","pron":"tah-ats-oo-maw'","derivation":"from H6105 (עָצַם);","strongs_