,"pron":"tap-poo'-akh","derivation":"the same as H8598 (תַּפּוּחַ);","strongs_def":"Tappuach, the name of two places in Palestine, also of an Israelite","kjv_def":"Tappuah.","pos":"proper locative noun, proper masculine noun","usage":"Tappuah(6x)"}}